        {"soussou": "fo nonon keme firin njondon", "english": "only about two hundred meters"}
      ],
      "position": "introduces exception"
    },
    {
      "word": "xa na mu a ra",
      "function": "adversative",
      "meaning": "if not that / otherwise",
      "examples": [
        {"soussou": "xa na mu a ra a de xabee seeti maxaba", "english": "if not his beard's side to shave"}
